   - `GET /api/uploads` — list uploads for tenant/document
   - `DELETE /api/uploads/:id` — delete file
   - `GET /api/files/:key+` — serve file from R2 (with auth check)

### 2. Editor Image Upload (2h)
1. `components/editor/image-upload.tsx`:
